ndation","devstats_url":"https://easegress.devstats.cncf.io/","lfx_slug":"easegress","maturity":"sandbox","repositories":[{"url":"https://github.com/easegress-io/easegress","primary":true}],"tag":["network"],"twitter_url":"https://twitter.com/megaease"},{"category":"Orchestration & Management","homepage_url":"https://emissary-ingress.dev/","id":"orchestration-management--api-gateway--emissary-ingress","logo":"logos/19518469b70b8e3e3789e07a400f80d60e89bdb23c8017b04515515bbda4f64e.svg","name":"Emissary-Ingress","subcategory":"API Gateway","website":"https://emissary-ingress.dev/","accepted_at":"2021-04-13","artwork_url":"https://github.com/cncf/artwork/tree/master/projects/emissary-ingress","clomonitor_name":"emissary-ingress","crunchbase_url":"https://www.crunchbase.com/organization/cloud-native-computing-foundation","devstats_url":"https://emissaryingress.devstats.cncf.io/","featured":{"label":"CNCF Incubating","order":2},"incubating_at":"2021-04-13","lfx_slug":"emissary","maturity":"incubating","repositories":[{"url":"https://github.com/emissary-ingress/emissary","primary":true}],"summary":{"business_use_case":"Emissary-Ingress speeds up deployment time and reduces the burden on platform teams by empowering developers to deploy new routes in a self-service manner. Platform/cloud teams can centrally manage hosts and certificates while developers can manage the resources relevant to them.","integration":"Telepresence, Linkerd, Istio, Argo Rollouts, Envoy, gRPC, OpenTelemetry, Curiefense","personas":["Platform Engineers","Architects"],"release_rate":"Monthly","tags":["ingress","api gateway","gateway","decentralized-operation","developer-friendly"],"use_case":"Emissary-Ingress is a k8s-native, Envoy-based API gateway. It is designed to allow teams to work in a more decentralized way than the traditional Ingress object. Emissary-Ingress can scan for its CRDs across all namespaces, so development teams can deploy new network routing rules along with the apps that use them, increasing velocity. Emissary-Ingress can be extended via API calls with authentication and rate limiting services. It is compatible with all the CNCF service meshes, and facilitates canary deployments when integrated with Argo Rollouts."},"tag":["network"]},{"category":"Orchestration & Management","homepage_url":"https://higress.io","id":"orchestration-management--api-gateway--higress","logo":"logos/3bfcf728193c733b68ebea17899885b1c2375f85b98bf53ea01fd769f1c1db77.svg","name":"Higress","subcategory":"API Gateway","website":"https://higress.io","accepted_at":"2026-03-15","additional_categories":[{"category":"AI Native Infra","subcategory":"Gateway"}],"crunchbase_url":"https://www.crunchbase.com/organization/cloud-native-computing-foundation","maturity":"sandbox","repositories":[{"url":"https://github.com/alibaba/higress","primary":true}],"tag":["network"]},{"category":"Orchestration & Management","homepage_url":"https://kgateway.dev/","id":"orchestration-management--api-gateway--kgateway","logo":"logos/563eeabb73cb8fa1d567f965ccf820dd9abecfada55a1e5cc9c45d5c587f40e6.svg","name":"Kgateway","subcategory":"API Gateway","website":"https://kgateway.dev/","accepted_at":"2025-03-04","additional_categories":[{"category":"AI Native Infra","subcategory":"Gateway"}],"artwork_url":"https://github.com/cncf/artwork/tree/master/projects/kgateway","blog_url":"https://kgateway.dev/blog","clomonitor_name":"kgateway","crunchbase_url":"https://www.crunchbase.com/organization/cloud-native-computing-foundation","description":"An Envoy-powered, Kubernetes-native API Gateway that integrates Kubernetes Gateway API with a control plane for API connectivity in any cloud environment.","devstats_url":"https://kgateway.devstats.cncf.io/","lfx_slug":"kgateway","maturity":"sandbox","repositories":[{"url":"https://github.com/kgateway-dev/kgateway","primary":true}],"summary":{"personas":["Platform Engineers","DevOps Engineers","SREs","API Managers"],"tags":["API Gateway","Envoy","Kubernetes","Gateway API","Cloud Native"],"use_case":"Kgateway is the most mature and widely deployed Envoy-based gateway in the market today. Built on open source  and open standards, kgateway integrates Kubernetes Gateway API with a control plane that scales from lightweight  microgateway deployments between services, to massively parallel centralized gateways handling billions of API calls,  to advanced AI gateway use cases for safety, security, and governance when integrating applications with third-party LLMs.  kgateway brings omni-directional API connectivity to any cloud and any environment. "},"tag":["network"]},{"category":"Orchestration & Management","homepage_url":"https://kuadrant.io","id":"orchestration-management--api-gateway--kuadrant","logo":"logos/4be4dfdc7c156747f9043a33139f7aa08a6c14e0cfa2e35e85d9bd0a43d553f7.svg","name":"Kuadrant","subcategory":"API Gateway","website":"https://kuadrant.io","accepted_at":"2024-06-19","artwork_url":"https://github.com/cncf/artwork/tree/master/projects/kuadrant","clomonitor_name":"kuadrant","crunchbase_url":"https://www.crunchbase.com/organization/cloud-native-computing-foundation","description":"Kuadrant combines Gateway API and Istio-based gateway controllers to enhance application connectivity. It enables platform engineers  and application developers to easily connect, secure, and protect their services and infrastructure across multiple clusters  with policies for TLS, DNS, application authentication & authorization, and rate limiting.","devstats_url":"https://kuadrant.devstats.cncf.io/","lfx_slug":"kuadrant","maturity":"sandbox","repositories":[{"url":"https://github.com/kuadrant/kuadrant-operator","primary":true}],"tag":["network"]},{"category":"Orchestration & Management","homepage_url":"https://www.aeraki.net/","id":"orchestration-management--service-mesh--aeraki-mesh","logo":"logos/59c6f1bd9eef9221d44e07e22b383a835d1f0af878803761ee3c3883a8e32112.svg","name":"Aeraki Mesh","subcategory":"Service Mesh","website":"https://www.aeraki.net/","accepted_at":"2022-06-17","artwork_url":"https://github.com/cncf/artwork/tree/master/projects/aerakimesh","blog_url":"https://www.aeraki.net/blog/","clomonitor_name":"aeraki-mesh","crunchbase_url":"https://www.crunchbase.com/organization/cloud-native-computing-foundation","description":"Aeraki Mesh allows you to manage any layer-7 traffic in a service mesh","devstats_url":"https://aerakimesh.devstats.cncf.io/","lfx_slug":"aerakimesh","maturity":"sandbox","latest_annual_review_at":"2023-08-14","latest_annual_review_url":"https://github.com/cncf/toc/pull/1143","repositories":[{"url":"https://github.com/aeraki-mesh/aeraki","primary":true}],"slack_url":"https://cloud-native.slack.com/messages/aeraki-mesh","summary":{"business_use_case":"While service mesh becomes an important infrastructure for microservices, many(if not all) service mesh implementations mainly focus on HTTP protocols and treat other protocols as plain TCP traffic. This is an obstacle for a lot of organizations when they try to leverage service mesh's promised capablities to simplify their microservice development and operation. Aeraki Mesh solve this problem by providing a common layer-7 service mesh framework both in data plane and control plane, which is built on top of Envoy and Istio and can work with them together very well.","integrations":"Istio, Envoy","personas":["SREs","DevOps Engineers","Architects"],"release_rate":"Every few months","tags":["Service Mesh"],"use_case":"Aeraki Mesh has been created to provide a non-intrusive, highly extendable way to manage any layer-7 traffic in a service mesh, including Dubbo, Thrift, bRPC, Redis, etc., and private protocols as well."},"tag":["network"]},{"category":"Orchestration & Management","homepage_url":"https://istio.io/","id":"orchestration-management--service-mesh--istio","logo":"logos/2d881599f6faed0a16840a675049bd10ce7096134d93df3f533aaf91972a9689.svg","name":"Istio","subcategory":"Service Mesh","website":"https://istio.io/","accept